2:T83d,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is HubSpot Operations Hub better than Make (Integromat)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. HubSpot Operations Hub scores 7.0 overall while Make (Integromat) scores 9.0. HubSpot Operations Hub is best for HubSpot users and revenue operations, while Make (Integromat) excels for power users and agencies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, HubSpot Operations Hub or Make (Integromat)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"HubSpot Operations Hub starts at Free and Make (Integromat) starts at Free. HubSpot Operations Hub offers a free plan. Make (Integromat) offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from HubSpot Operations Hub to Make (Integromat)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both HubSpot Operations Hub and Make (Integromat) support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about HubSpot Operations Hub vs Make (Integromat)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, HubSpot Operations Hub holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Make (Integromat) has an overall rating of 9/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise HubSpot Operations Hub for deep hubspot crm integration and Make (Integromat) for superior visual workflow builder."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, HubSpot Operations Hub or Make (Integromat)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Make (Integromat) for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, HubSpot Operations Hub remains a stron