flow builder."}]]}],["$","div","4",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-q","children":"Which should I choose in 2026, HubSpot Operations Hub or Make (Integromat)?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-a","children":"In 2026, we recommend Make (Integromat) for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, HubSpot Operations Hub remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize deep hubspot crm integration. Try both free trials before committing."}]]}]]}]
